#

Creamy Truffle Mashed Potatoes

35 min
$8.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Side Dish

Tags:

Comfort FoodSide DishVegetarian

Description

Indulge in these rich and creamy mashed potatoes infused with the luxurious flavor of truffle oil for a gourmet touch.

Ingredients

  • potatoes: 2 lbs
  • butter: 4 tbsp
  • heavy cream: 1/2 cup
  • truffle oil: 2 tbsp
  • salt: 1 tsp
  • pepper: 1/2 tsp
  • chives (optional): 2 tbsp, chopped
